  "page": "Robyn Ryswell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\"><img alt=\"House Ryswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/50px-House_Ryswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/75px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/100px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Robyn Ryswell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">House Ryswell</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nor after <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_141_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">141&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Jonnel_Stark\" title=\"Jonnel Stark\">Jonnel Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Robyn Ryswell</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">House Ryswell</a> during the latter half of the second century after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robyn_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Robyn married <a href=\"/index.php/Jonnel_Stark\" title=\"Jonnel Stark\">Jonnel Stark</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> after the death of his first wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark_(daughter_of_Rickon)\" title=\"Sansa Stark (daughter of Rickon)\">Sansa Stark</a>, but they had no issue.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-wives_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-wives-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robyn_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Calculation-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued3)#Robyn_Ryswell\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued3)\">Robyn Ryswell</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Appendix: Stark Lineage.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-wives-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-wives_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">asoiaf.westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/152844-the-wiki-timeline-project-v2/&amp;page=5&amp;tab=comments#comment-8495243\">The Wiki-Timeline Project v2 &#8211; Comment by Ran (March 16, 2020)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succes